sub_title: Chemical-Pharmaceutical Quality Assessor of new Medicine at CBG, the Dutch Medicines Evaluation Board
summary: Currently finishing my PhD project promotion in the PhD4Glycodrug project, both at the University of Ljubljana, Slovenia and at Lund University in Sweden. I have applied computer-aided drug design, pharmacokinetic analyses and my expertise in organic chemistry to synthesize small molecule inhibitors of biological relevance in Galectin-8 research.
